Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Apartment block to be sold in-one-line

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE as the exclusive sales agent is pleased to present 2 Sutherland Street, Cremorne.  The property is a well maintained three storey residential apartment block sitting on a large 1,235sqm* parcel of land with significant development potential. The property commands an elevated position enjoying breath taking views of Cammeray Golf Course and water views of Willoughby Bay. Boasting a north westerly aspect & 3 street frontages, the property is bathed in natural light. 

The property benefits from the following key attributes:
•	22 unit apartment block with 21 car spaces
•	944sqm* of NSA
•	Significant luxury development opportunity
•	R4 High Density Residential Zoning with 12m Height Limit
•	Enjoying water views over Willoughby Bay and views Cammeray Golf Course
•	Ideally located in an affluent downsizer market
•	Easily accessible by three street frontages
•	Highly sought-after suburb close to Sydney CBD
•	Within walking distance to local transport, Cremorne retail strip, restaurants and schools.


2 Sutherland Street, Cremorne will be sold via expressions of interest closing on Wednesday, 16 October 2019 at 4:00pm.

For more information or to request access to the due diligence room, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

*Approximate

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: DA approved for 20 units & 22 car spaces
Unique design setback from Military Road

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
PREMIUM LOCATION CLOSE TO SHOPS, TRANSPORT, SCHOOLS AND PARKS

CBRE is pleased to present 211 Military Road, Cremorne to market. This residential development site has been DA approved for 20 luxury units with 2 levels of basement car parking. Located around the corner from Neutral Bay’s main retail strip, the property benefits from a prime location in Sydney’s Lower North Shore.

211 Military Road, Cremorne capitalises on the following key attributes: 

- Land area: 1,008sqm*
- DA approved for 20 residential units with car and bike parking
- R4 High Density Residential zoning
- 12 metre height limit
- Currently a two storey apartment block with four units
- Buses to the Sydney CBD available just 100m* from the property
- Metres from Neutral Bay’s main retail strip
- 3.6km* from Sydney CBD
- Highly demanded suburb with strong growth and affluent demographic

*Approximate

211 Military Road, Cremorne will be made available for sale via expressions of interest closing on Wednesday, 14 March 2018 at 4:00pm.

For further details, please contact the exclusive CBRE selling agents.
